<C>__{chris}
<D>__{what are you doing up? it's three thirty in the morning.}
<C>__{ron}
<D>__{heard you get up off the couch half an hour ago, and had a funny feeling you might not be here for our breakfast.}
<A>__{chris says nothing.}
<C>__{ron }
